{"type": "user", "message": {"role": "user", "content": "/second-brain-wiki Ingest this into my wiki:\n\n# Prompt Engineering Best Practices\n\nKey techniques for writing effective prompts:\n- Be specific about the output format you want\n- Provide examples of good and bad output\n- Use chain-of-thought for complex reasoning tasks\n- Break multi-step tasks into sequential prompts\n- Include constraints and boundaries explicitly\n\nSource: Internal team discussion, 2026-06-15"}, "timestamp": "2026-07-09T15:38:43.632Z"}
